{"tid":1496571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你被拘留但又入咗醫院","createTime":"2019-08-22T14:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:39:06.000Z","uid":204615,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cb590e54018611ff26077da4f45e799d6cc8d0d3","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"醫管局對醫護人員出咗個小錦囊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqL2Z1A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqL2Z1A.jpg&h=ece83cff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3ckMGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3ckMGA.jpg&h=ffca5b54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWBE2eW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWBE2eW.jpg&h=e91fe39c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wPCOUW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wPCOUW.jpg&h=5b058282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為醫護人員，我地一定會同各方人士好好合作，但都會盡力以病人權益為先。<br />\n<br />\n有一D資料，入院時醫講人員係一定會問你，例如緊急聯絡人資料、個人病歷史、有冇曾經出現過食物/藥物敏感......<br />\n<br />\n其中<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇曾經出現過食物/藥物敏感</span></span>呢樣野係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極為重要</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有懷疑一定要搞清楚</span></span>！但有時如果你係好細個嘅情況下，或者係純粹唔記得咗有冇發生過，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你嘅家人同朋友就可能可以幫到手clarify</span></span>. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁作為一個盡責嘅醫講人員就需要幫你打電話問家人/朋友，請佢地提供資料</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n記住，食物/藥物敏感資料真係好重要，每次入院都要update, 因為誤服致敏嘅食/藥物係可以死亡。而我本人就有藥物敏感，但到咗我大個咗先記得係乜野藥同埋update 返個資料。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好睇少食物藥物敏感嘅重要性！唔肯定就一定要搞清楚，好多時家人朋友都可以幫到手！"},{"pid":"dcd717e483679f8c026fd3552f152dcf42308823","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"Shit! 開錯時事台！"},{"pid":"34b82a5ef256a9c66bfd1800bab3b8702230bbd6","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:51:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫手推到連仔睇到？"},{"pid":"f6d7aee39b332349e3e4b81e952a03955d99a47e","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"我想轉返台"},{"pid":"e38daeb9e3e5e7ddc9aadde8bc5e9f6a830cb060","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:51:53.000Z","msg":"健康台好似先啱"},{"pid":"2870d551699602d25542ca45e85a0959cc7fe1ec","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"定係應該吹水台會多D人睇到？"},{"pid":"332d07b38ebdd306e5027162b30fade640774999","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"但如果轉咗去吹水台，會唔會有人以為我吹水？"},{"pid":"269cd9e04aca804ec55bb9de6166cdf63a5a8591","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"食物藥物敏感真係好重要，唔可以忽視"},{"pid":"4d285af1bad934215c3b73dcdac01abda66f49f8","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"冇得是但答"},{"pid":"0b584effa061e86e6f9f347f2abe52993fecd199","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以幫我諗到轉乜台？"},{"pid":"222c4766115f222cd310123c02dba93ea12dc0ca","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"同埋搵到人幫我轉台？"},{"pid":"a810bd2fa98646aa2bc4a193886d392a1b77198d","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:56:27.000Z","msg":"完全冇人重視呢一樣野"},{"pid":"4afa531a68768ae05034e78ff496150d126dc78d","tid":1496571,"uid":204615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc5f1fd4